testsuite.name: au.org.ala.ecodata.PermissionsControllerSpec

testcase.name: canUserEditProjects: when not all parameters are passed
A user can be assigned a role for a program
All parameters must be supplied when assigning a user a program role
A valid role must be supplied when assigning a user a program role
A user can have a role unassigned for a program
All parameters must be supplied when unassigning a user from a program role
the members of a program can be returned
the member of programs can be returned in batches
A valid role must be supplied when unassigning a user from a program role
A user can be assigned a role for a hub
All parameters must be supplied when assigning a user a hub role
A valid role must be supplied when assigning a user a hub role
A user can have a role unassigned from a hub
All parameters must be supplied when unassigning a user from a hub role
A valid role must be supplied when unassigning a user from a hub role
